# Cantrips


# Spellbooks
spellbook-spellbook-blink-name = Blink Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-blink-description = Don't blink or you'll miss yourself teleporting away.

spellbook-spellbook-fireball-name = Fireball Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-fireball-description = Get most crew exploding with rage when they see this fireball heading toward them!

spellbook-spellbook-force-wall-name = Force Wall Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-force-wall-description = Make three walls of pure force that you can pass through, but others can't.

spellbook-spellbook-knock-name = Knock Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-knock-description = Opens all airlocks, crates and lockers nearby.

spellbook-spellbook-smite-name = Smite Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-smite-description = Don't like them? EXPLODE them into giblets!

spellbook-spellbook-spawn-name = Spawn Spellbook
spellbook-spellbook-spawn-description = Conjure forth three magicarp, to your aid or to your detriment!


# Wands and staves
spellbook-wand-rgb-staff-name = RGB Staff
spellbook-wand-rgb-staff-description = Add some color to everyone's life, turning anything that glows into a rainbow display!

spellbook-wand-instant-death-name = Magical Wand of Instant Death
spellbook-wand-instant-death-description = Fires a fast projectile killing anyone that it touches! Much more civilized than barbaric firearms.

spellbook-wand-cluwne-polymorph-name = Wand of Cluwning
spellbook-wand-cluwne-polymorph-description = For when you really hate someone and Smite isn't enough.

spellbook-wand-bread-polymorph-name = Magic Bread Wand
spellbook-wand-bread-polymorph-description = Trap your enemies in the rising power of gluten.

spellbook-wand-monkey-polymorph-name = Wand of Monkey Polymorph
spellbook-wand-monkey-polymorph-description = Return to monke.

spellbook-wand-healing-staff-name = Staff of Healing
spellbook-wand-healing-staff-description = Good for helping others, and covering up accidental boo-boos.


# Enchanted equipment
spellbook-armor-name = Enchanted Breastplate
spellbook-armor-description = A highly protective breastplate master crafted by only the system's finest mages. Does *not* count as robes.
